1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Welcome. This quick tour shows a simple way to move through the app with clarity.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:09,000
Step one: start at the dashboard, review your progress, and choose what needs attention.

3
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:14,000
Step two: set an intention, goal, or plan so the next action has direction.

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:21,000
Step three: add a practice entry in whichever area fits your day.

5
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:27,000
Capture what happened, what you learned, and what you want to carry forward.

6
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:33,000
Step four: review insights, trends, and recommendations so progress becomes visible.

7
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:41,000
Step five: use Autograph Exchange. Create a profile, request or give an autograph, and preserve meaningful moments.

8
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:46,000
Share, join community spaces, tune settings, manage data, and keep the experience running smoothly.

9
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:51,000
Begin with one small entry. Let steady use turn intention into momentum.
